t Continuous Tense)</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_tuong_lai_tiep_dien_Future_Continuous_Tense\" title=\"Thì tương lai tiếp diễn (Future Continuous Tense)\">Thì tương lai tiếp diễn (Future Continuous Tense)</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_hoan_thanh_Perfect_Tense\" title=\"Thì hoàn thành (Perfect Tense)\">Thì hoàn thành (Perfect Tense)</a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_qua_khu_hoan_thanh_Past_Perfect_Tense\" title=\"Thì quá khứ hoàn thành (Past Perfect Tense)\">Thì quá khứ hoàn thành (Past Perfect Tense)</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_hien_tai_hoan_thanh_Present_Perfect_Tense\" title=\"Thì hiện tại hoàn thành (Present Perfect Tense)\">Thì hiện tại hoàn thành (Present Perfect Tense)</a></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_tuong_lai_hoan_thanh_Future_Perfect_Tense\" title=\"Thì tương lai hoàn thành (Future Perfect Tense)\">Thì tương lai hoàn thành (Future Perfect Tense)</a></li></ul></li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/dau-hieu-nhan-biet-cac-thi-trong-tieng-anh/#Thi_hoan_thanh_tiep_dien_Perfect_Continuous_Tense\" title=\"Thì hoàn thành tiếp diễn (Perfect Continuous Tense)\">Thì hoàn thành tiếp diễn (Perfect Continuous Tense)</a><ul class='ez-to